@anchor{Generic-Function drei-base:capitalize-region}
@deffn {Generic Function} {drei-base:capitalize-region} mark1 mark2
@findex drei-base:capitalize-region
Capitalize all words after mark1 and before mark2.
An error is signaled if the two marks are positioned in different buffers.
It is acceptable to pass an offset in place of one of the marks.
@end deffn
